'''TYC 8998-760-1'''是一个年轻的恆星，於{{val|1700|u=万年}}前誕生，位于[[苍蝇座|苍蝇座]]，距离[[地球|地球]]约310光年，质量是太阳的{{val|1.00|0.02}}倍。

它的年龄约为1700万岁，处于[[G型主序星|G2V]]光谱型主序星的年龄下限。TYC 8998-760-1有兩个系外行星，是与[[太阳系|太阳系]]相近的[[行星系统|行星系统]]中，最接近太阳系的。相比之下，太阳的年龄是{{val|450000|fmt=commas|u=万年}}，約為TYC 8998-760-1的250倍。所有G2V光谱型主序星的估计寿命约有{{val|100|fmt=commas|u=亿年}}。

==行星系统==
TYC 8998-760-1有两个巨大的系外行星绕恒星运行。由[[ESO|ESO]]的[[甚大望远镜|甚大望远镜]]使用其[[光谱-高对比度系外行星研究|光谱-高对比度系外行星研究]]仪器拍摄了它們。這是第一次直接拍攝到多个行星圍繞类似恆星太阳运行的图像。<ref name="ESO_Bohn">{{cite web |last1=ESO/Bohn |title=First ever image of a multi-planet system around a Sun-like star (uncropped, with annotations) |url=https://www.eso.org/public/images/eso2011b/ |website=ESO |publisher=European Space Agency |accessdate=2020-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724161316/https://www.eso.org/public/images/eso2011b/ |archivedate=2020-07-24 |date=2020-07-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Wall">{{cite news |last=Wall |first=Mike |title=Multiplanet system around sunlike star photographed for 1st time ever - The two newly imaged planets are huge — 14 and 6 times more massive than Jupiter. |url=https://www.space.com/multiplanet-system-sun-like-star-first-photo.html |date=2020-07-22 |work=Space.com |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2020-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722180729/https://www.space.com/multiplanet-system-sun-like-star-first-photo.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

'''TYC 8998-760-1 b'''是一个行星，质量为[[木星|木星]]的14倍，半径为{{Jupiter radius|3}}。它以{{cvt|162|AU}}的距离公转，略遠于太阳与海王星距离的5倍。<ref name=bohn2020/><ref>{{Cite web|title=Astronomers Directly Image Two Giant Exoplanets around Young Sun-Like Star {{!}} Astronomy {{!}} Sci-News.com|url=http://www.sci-news.com/astronomy/directly-imaged-multi-planet-system-young-sun-like-star-08665.html|access-date=2020-07-25|website=Breaking Science News {{!}} Sci-News.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724050955/http://www.sci-news.com/astronomy/directly-imaged-multi-planet-system-young-sun-like-star-08665.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

'''TYC 8998-760-1 c'''是一个行星，质量为{{Jupiter mass|6}}，并以{{cvt|320|AU}}的距离公转，略遠于太阳与海王星距离的11倍。<ref name=bohn2020>{{cite journal |author=Bohn, Alexander |title=Two Directly Imaged, Wide-orbit Giant Planets around the Young, Solar Analog TYC 8998-760-1 |date=2020-07-22|journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal_Letters|The Astrophysical Journal Letters]] |volume=898 |number=1 |pages=L16 |doi=10.3847/2041-8213/aba27e | arxiv=2007.10991|bibcode=2020ApJ...898L..16B }}</ref>

